7.Describe the process of launching an EC2 instance.

     Launching an EC2 instance involves several key steps:

1. Sign in to AWS Management Console

2. Navigate to EC2 Dashboard 

3. Launch Instance
 - Click on “Launch Instance.”
 - Choose an Amazon Machine Image (AMI) that serves as a template for your instance.

4. Select Instance Type

5. Configure Instance Details

6. Add Storage

7. Add Tags

8. Configure Security Group

9. Review and Launch

10. Select or Create Key Pair

11. Launch

12. Access the Instance


